# Future Literature Queries

Suggested queries for PaperQA2 - these are in a special format with "Project", "question containing "keywords" in quotes embedded within the question", 3 relevant DOI's separated by commas.
for example:
HippoTail, What evidence supports a "connectivity" "gradient" along the "longitudinal axis of the hippocampus", particularly distinguishing "anterior hippocampus" from "posterior hippocampus" in humans?, https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.2422083122, https://doi.org/10.1073/pnas.2101743118, https://doi.org/10.7554/eLife.76143

